Discount Considers $138 Million Retirement Package, Ma’ariv Says

-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 
2011-03-07T06:41:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-07/discount-considers-138-million-retirement-package-ma-ariv-says.html
  Israel Discount Bank Ltd. (DSCT)  is
considering offering staff a retirement package that would
include 500 employees and cost as much as 500 million shekels
($138 million), the daily Ma’ariv said, without saying where it
got the information.   A spokeswoman for the bank declined to comment on the
article.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gwen Ackerman at 
 gackerman@bloomberg.net  